<div class="clearfix">
	<div class='grid_12'>					<div class="post clearfix" id="post-11738">
				<div class='post-thumbnail'><a href='http://www.mendel.ca/'><img width="940" height="320" src="http://www.mendel.ca/cms/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Mendel-at-night.jpg" class="attachment-single-post-thumbnail-940 wp-post-image" alt="Mendel at night" /></a></div>				<h2 class="posttitle">Thank you, Saskatoon!</h2>
				<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The Mendel Art Gallery has closed as we prepare for the opening of <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://remaimodern.org">Remai Modern</a></span> in 2017. On behalf of current and past board, staff, members and volunteers – thank you for 50 years of wonderful memories. Information on <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.mendel.ca/category/exhibitions/">past exhibitions</a></span> at the Mendel remains available for your research. For inquiries related to the Mendel Art Gallery, please contact <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="mailto:mendel@mendel.ca">mendel@mendel.ca</a></span>.</p>
<p>The Civic Conservatory remains open to the public. The Mendel Building will be transformed into a <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.museumforkids.sk.ca/">Children’s Discovery Museum</a></span>, tentatively scheduled to open in 2018.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>Remai Modern is becoming…</h2>
<p>Learn more about <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://remaimodern.org">Remai Modern</a></span>, scheduled to open in 2017, including details on our <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://remaimodern.org/prelaunch">Pre-launch programs</a></span> that are already rolling out.</p>
<p>Subscribe for project updates</p>
